---
import SideForm from "./SideForm.astro";
---

<!-- faq-area start -->
<div class="ab-tabs pt-110 pb-120">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-xxl-10">
        <div class="section_title_wrapper text-center mb-50 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s" style="visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.3s; animation-name: fadeInUp;">
          <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
   <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xxl-8 col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-8 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s" style="visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.3s; animation-name: fadeInUp;">
        <div class="tab-content mb-30" id="pills-tabContent">
            <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="pills-home-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-home-tab-1">
                <div class="faq-content faq-white">
                    <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample-1">
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <p class="h2 oswald accordion-header" id="headingOne-1">
                                <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne-1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne-1">
                                  Why should I study in the United States?
                                </button>
                            </p>
                            <div id="collapseOne-1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne-1" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample-1">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <p>Studying in the United States provides you access to several outstanding institutions and schools. American degrees are renowned across the world, and you may choose from a variety of programs that will allow you to learn and do research.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <p class="h2 oswald accordion-header" id="headingTwo-1">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo-1">
                                  How can I apply to study in the United States?
                                </button>
                            </p>
                            <div id="collapseTwo-1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo-1" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample-1">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <p>To study in the United States, you must apply directly to the institutions or colleges that you wish to attend. First, learn about the schools and the programs they offer. Then, fill out their online forms, send them your school grades and English test scores, and pay whatever costs they need.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <p class="h2 oswald accordion-header" id="headingThree-1">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree-1">
                                  What are the eligibility requirements for studying in the United States?
                                </button>
                            </p>
                            <div id="collapseThree-1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree-1" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample-1">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <p>Each school and program has its own set of standards, although you normally need strong grades (such as a high school diploma or a degree), to demonstrate that you speak English effectively (by a test such as TOEFL or IELTS), and, in some cases, to take a test such as the SAT or ACT.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <p class="h2 oswald accordion-header" id="headingThree1-1">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree1-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree1-1">
                                  Can I work while studying in the United States?
                                </button>
                            </p>
                            <div id="collapseThree1-1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree1-1" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample-1">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <p>Yes, if you have an F-1 student visa, you may work part-time on campus during the school year and full-time during breaks. Some students may also work off-campus if it is connected to their studies or part of a particular program.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <p class="h2 oswald accordion-header" id="headingThree2-1">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree2-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree2-1">
                                  How can I apply for an F-1 student visa to study in the United States?
                                </button>
                            </p>
                            <div id="collapseThree2-1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree2-1" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample-1">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <p>To obtain an F-1 student visa, you must have an admission letter from a US institution or college. You must also establish that you have enough money to cover tuition and living expenses, have a valid passport, and may be required to attend an interview at the US consulate. Apply online, pay the cost, and provide fingerprints if requested.                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xxl-4 col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-md-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.5s" style="visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.5s; animation-name: fadeInUp;">
        <SideForm />
    </div>
</div>

  </div>
</div>
<!-- faq-area end -->